     <lb/><space unit="cm" quantity="0.2"/>Chez <publisher><name>Guillaume Cavellat</name></publisher>, Libraire juré, de-
       <lb rend="hyphen"/>mourant à l&#x2019;enseigne de la <placeName type="enseigne">Poulle grasse</placeName>, devant
       <lb/>le <placeName type="batiment">college de <placeName type="ville">Cambrai</placeName></placeName>.
